@startuml
left to right direction
!theme plain
skinparam nodesep 50
skinparam ranksep 50

node "Cliente Web" as WebClient

node "Cliente de Godot" as GodotClient
node "Servidor Web" as WebServer

node "Servidor de Backend" as Backend

database "Servidor de Base de Datos" as DB

WebClient --> WebServer : HTTP/HTTPS
WebServer --> Backend : Rest API / WebSockets
GodotClient --> Backend : Rest API / WebSockets

Backend --> DB : Persiste y recupera información

@enduml
